&uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>gan gaz d&uuml;z&uuml;mini&#328; der&#328;ewi&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Orak &ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;k ganazlygyny &yacute;a-da
be&yacute;leki gemoglobinopati&yacute;alary &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykarmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>gemoglobin elektroforezi&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Bikanun psihoaktiw dermanlary ulanmakda g&uuml;man
edil&yacute;&auml;n &yacute;agda&yacute;ynda&nbsp;<b>pe&#351;ewi&#328; we
gany&#328; toksikologiki barlagy&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Funksi&yacute;a,
radiasi&yacute;a we instrumental diagnostika</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&#351;emiki we arterial priapizmi diferensial anyklamak we
fistulany&#328; lokalizasi&yacute;asy &uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>penisi&#328; we
perineumy&#328; re&#328;kli dupleks ultrases barlagy&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Korpora kavernozasyny&#328; tekiz my&#351;salaryny&#328;
howpsuzlygyny &ccedil;aklamak we erektil funksi&yacute;any dikeltmek&nbsp;<b>&uuml;&ccedil;in
jyns agzalaryny&#328; magnit-rezonans tomografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Embolizasi&yacute;a wagtynda arterial priapizmi bejermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>pudendal arteri&yacute;any&#328; sa&yacute;lama
arteriografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Korpora kavernozasyna ga&yacute;taryp bolmajak zeper
&yacute;etmegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak &uuml;&ccedil;in
ereksi&yacute;any we agyryny &yacute;ok etmek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;
&yacute;oly we gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Priapizmi&#328;
h&uuml;j&uuml;mi &uuml;&ccedil;in otur&yacute;an salkyn hammamlar ulanylyp
bilner.&nbsp;Ativea-da bolmasa, sowuk kompressleri i&ccedil;ege me&yacute;danyna
&ccedil;aly&#328;.&nbsp;Jyns agzalaryny&#328; yzyna ga&yacute;taryp bolmajak
&uuml;&yacute;tgemelerinden ga&ccedil;a durmak &uuml;&ccedil;in gysga wagtda
lukman&ccedil;ylyk k&ouml;megi maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>I&#351;emiki
priapizm&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&uuml;&ccedil;in derman bejergisi&nbsp;,
wazokonstriktor dermanlaryny (&nbsp;<i>simpatomimetika &yacute;a-da
alfa-adrenerjik agonistleri&nbsp;</i>)&nbsp;i&ccedil;erki
administrasi&yacute;any&nbsp;we&nbsp;<i>gan &yacute;ygnamagyny azald&yacute;an
dermanlary&nbsp;</i>kabul&nbsp;<i>etmegi&nbsp;</i>,&nbsp;<b>i&#351;emiki
d&auml;l priapizmi&nbsp;</b>-&nbsp;<i>agyry kesiji seri&#351;deleri &ouml;z
i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar&nbsp;</i>.&nbsp;<b>Orak
&ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;klerini&#328;&nbsp;pri&yacute;apizmini&nbsp;</b>bejermekde
a&yacute;ratyn &ccedil;&auml;reler,&nbsp;ymtylma we dyn&ccedil; aly&#351;
&uuml;&ccedil;in ta&yacute;ynlyk&nbsp;<i>bilen ne&#351;e analjeziklerini&#328;
damar&nbsp;</i><b>damarlaryny&nbsp;</b>&ouml;z i&ccedil;ine
al&yacute;ar&nbsp;.&nbsp;Mundan ba&#351;ga-da, go&#351;ma&ccedil;a&nbsp;<i>oksijen
tedavisi we bikarbonatlar bilen gan alkalinization&nbsp;</i>zerur bolan&nbsp;,
&#351;e&yacute;le hem,&nbsp;<i>aly&#351;-&ccedil;aly&#351; nakli&nbsp;</i>dokumalary
oksijen bo&yacute;un artdyrmak maksady
bilen.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Perineuma buz sepmek &yacute;a-da perine&yacute;i gysmak (esasanam
&ccedil;agalarda t&auml;sirli).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Penile gysy&#351; sindromyny &ccedil;&ouml;zmek &uuml;&ccedil;in
durgun gany akdyrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in korpora kavernozany&#328;
&#351;orla&#351;magy (arassalanmagy).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&yacute;lanyp ge&ccedil;mek operasi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, jyns
agzasyndan gan akmagy &uuml;&ccedil;in emeli &yacute;ol d&ouml;retmekdir.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Embolizasi&yacute;a&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, jyns agzalaryny&#328;&nbsp;<b>deri&nbsp;</b>arteri&yacute;asyny&#328;
diametrini azaltmak &uuml;&ccedil;in amala a&#351;yryl&yacute;an minimal
invaziv operasi&yacute;a.&nbsp;Patologiki ta&yacute;dan &uuml;&yacute;tgedilen
gan ak&yacute;an &yacute;erine bir turba salyn&yacute;ar, onu&#328; &uuml;sti
bilen &yacute;elimle&yacute;ji ergin sanjyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;G&auml;mini&#328;
diwarynda go&#351;ma&ccedil;a gatlak emele getir&yacute;&auml;r, netijede
g&auml;mi daral&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu, jyns agzalaryna gan a&yacute;lany&#351;yny
peseld&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Prostetika.&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Jyns agzalaryny&#328; yzyna
ga&yacute;taryp bolmajak &uuml;&yacute;tgemeleri bilen, erektil
funksi&yacute;any dikeltmegi&#328; &yacute;eke-t&auml;k usuly falloprostetika.&nbsp;Gurlu&#351;y
&uuml;pj&uuml;n ed&yacute;&auml;n enjam, jyns agzalaryna
&yacute;erle&#351;diril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bir adama n&auml;&ccedil;e ir
lukman&ccedil;ylyk k&ouml;megi berilse, priapizmden so&#328; kuwwatyny doly
dikeltmek has &auml;htimaldyr.&nbsp;Intakyn durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
&yacute;okarlandyrmak we patologiki agyryly ereksi&yacute;any&#328;
ga&yacute;talan&yacute;an h&uuml;j&uuml;mlerini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni
almak &uuml;&ccedil;in m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>ilkinji h&uuml;j&uuml;mde &ouml;z wagtynda lukmana &yacute;&uuml;z
tutu&#328; - terapi&yacute;a ilkinji 3-4 sagady&#328; dowamynda has
t&auml;sirli bol&yacute;ar;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; &#351;ikeslenmeginden ga&ccedil;a
duru&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;n dermanlary lukmany&#328;yzy&#328;
g&ouml;rkezmesi bo&yacute;un&ccedil;a kabul edi&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Eger bir adam gi&ccedil;
urolog-androlog lukmanyna &yacute;&uuml;z tutsa we uzak wagtlap
i&#351;emi&yacute;a seb&auml;pli jyns agzalaryny&#328; gurlu&#351;lary
dolulygyna za&yacute;alanan bolsa, priapizm h&uuml;j&uuml;minden so&#328;
g&uuml;&yacute;j&uuml;&#328; dikeldilmegi di&#328;e operasi&yacute;a (falloprostetika)
arkaly m&uuml;mkindir.&nbsp;Operasi&yacute;a gowy netijeleri ber&yacute;&auml;r
we &yacute;a&#351;yna garamazdan doly durmu&#351;da &yacute;a&#351;amaga
m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Zenanlary&#328; yzy.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Megalofalliki deformasi&yacute;a.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Jyns agzalaryny&#328; gysgalmagy we &yacute;itmegi m&uuml;mkin.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri &ccedil;anak we jyns organlarynda gan
a&yacute;lany&#351;ygyny&#328; &yacute;aramazla&#351;magyna seb&auml;p
bol&yacute;an faktorlary &yacute;ok etm&auml;ge
g&ouml;n&uuml;kdirilendir.&nbsp;Priapizmi&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak
&uuml;&ccedil;in:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>gematologiki we &yacute;&uuml;rek-damar kesellerini wagtynda
bejermek;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>di&#328;e lukmany&#328; g&ouml;rkezmesi bo&yacute;un&ccedil;a
antihipertansif dermanlary we g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lendiriji stimullary kabul
edi&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>i&#351;je&#328; durmu&#351; &yacute;&ouml;relgesini
&yacute;a&#351;amak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>alkogol we ne&#351;e seri&#351;delerini i&ccedil;megi bes
edi&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>jyns agzalaryna we perine&yacute; &#351;ikeslerinden ga&ccedil;a
duru&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
